{'id': 18312915, 'body': "Hey Friend. Thanks for the honest feedback. We appreciate it as it helps us make the app better for all of our members. It sounds like your running into a micro deposit verification issue. This can take up to 3 business days to verify, and anything past that won't be verified.

Let's get you back into your account and help make it right.
Please reach out to Dave's team at davecares@dave.com and mention App Review in the title of your email so we can identify you and we can help you out with this right away.", 'modified': '2020-10-06T23:27:50Z'}

{'id': 2880010, 'body': "Hey there Blvckrep!

Please reach out to Dave's team at friends@dave.com so that we can take a look at your account specifically. 
Also if our $1 membership has over-drafted you, please include a screenshot so that we can check into other ways that we can help.", 'modified': '2018-03-20T18:12:22Z'}

{'id': 1860217, 'body': "Thanks for your review, Shelby5642! 

I think you'll be happy to hear that we're launching an improvement this week that makes it easier to verify your paydays on the fly and that should lead to quicker and more reliable advances!

Also, we were able to reduce that $160 to $115. Here's an article that explains it a little more: http://help.dave.com/error-messages-in-plain-english/for-your-safety-i-need-to-see-a-cushion-of-at-least-115-the-day-after-your-last-2-paydays", 'modified': '2017-11-27T18:39:38Z'}

